# Patients put at risk by EU laws on working time, doctors warn

Trainee doctors are 'not getting enough experience because of stifling effect
of working time directive'

  *     * Tweet this
    *     * ![](http://static.guim.co.uk/static/534a025fbd5b6ca3cafea5df66abf4d49b01b6fd/common/images/icon_reddit.gif) reddit this

  * James Meikle

  * guardian.co.uk, Thursday 12 January 2012 09.58 GMT
